- Just for you.

91
00:06:44.468 --> 00:06:48.347
- It's beautiful.
- Beautiful golden tilefish. line-caught.

92
00:06:48.556 --> 00:06:49.890
- Beautiful.
- Give me a kiss.

93
00:06:50.141 --> 00:06:52.017
- Bob.
- Give me a kiss.

94
00:06:52.643 --> 00:06:56.272
